feat(p04): complete multipers bifiltration pipeline + scale sensitivity + results

Adds P04 multi-parameter PH implementation with full production pipeline:
- Core module: multipers_bifiltration.py (bifiltration, signed measure, nulls)
- Scripts: p04_run_nulls.py, p04_run_5k.py, p04_explore_discretisation.py, p04_appendix_b.py
- Tests: test_multipers_validation.py, test_p04_embedding_stability.py  
- Results: p04_multipers/ (2k landmarks + 999 perms), p04_multipers_5k/, p04_exploration/
- Figures: null distributions, baseline comparison, regime income, Hilbert/rank analysis
- Paper drafts: v2-v4, LaTeX main, archive of v1

Implements income-stratified TDA for trajectory poverty trap detection.
Enables P04 submission (Sociological Methodology target).
